      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition, and we want to give you an honest, complete picture of what you're getting. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains a healthy shine with only minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with normal use. There are no significant dents or rust concerns, and the body lines look solid. The interior is clean and functional, showing moderate wear on the seats and high-touch surfaces, but nothing that detracts from everyday comfort. Mechanically, the vehicle runs reliably \u2014 the engine starts smoothly, the transmission shifts without issue, and all major systems are in good working order. Some routine maintenance items may be coming due, and we encourage a pre-purchase inspection so you can feel fully confident in your decision. Overall, this is a dependable, well-maintained vehicle that offers solid value for a buyer looking for a reliable daily driver without the premium price of a mint-condition unit.",
